<div class="hero-unit" style="text-align:center">
  <h1>Cl<span class="light">oud</span> A<span class="light">udio</span> 
    W<span class="light">orkstation</span></h1>
  <p>
    Listen, edit and manage your musical projects from anywhere. Share. 
    Collaborate.
  </p>
  <%= link_to "login", new_user_session_path, :class => "btn btn-primary btn-large btn-inverse" %>
  <%= link_to "sign up", new_user_registration_path, :class => "btn btn-primary btn-large" %>
</div>

<div class="row concepts">
  <div class="span3 accordion">
    <h3>Work from anywhere.</h3>
    <div id="work-from-anywhere" class="accordion-body collapse">
      Use Claw to work on your musical projects from anywhere. Upload your 
      tracks. Edit them via a web based multi-track sequencer. Work together
      with your band
    </div>
    <a class="accordion-toggle btn btn-mini pull-right btn-inverse" data-toggle="collapse" 
       href="#work-from-anywhere">
      <span class="caret"></span> learn more
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="span3 accordion">
    <h3>No more "ping pong".</h3>
    <div id="no-more-ping-pong" class="accordion-body collapse">
      A version control system allows you to work in parallel, compare, 
      restore and merge different song versions. <br />
      You can also comment songs and tracks, create/assign tasks, etc.
    </div>
    <a class="accordion-toggle btn btn-mini pull-right btn-inverse" data-toggle="collapse" 
       href="#no-more-ping-pong">
      <span class="caret"></span> learn more
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="span3 accordion">
    <h3>
      <span style="text-decoration:line-through">"Yet another DAW"</span>.
    </h3>
    <div id="not-yet-another-daw" class="accordion-body collapse">
      Claw is not "yet another DAW". The aim is to complete the tools we 
      already use and make it possible to collaborate with people using 
      different DAW. Still, the web interface has elementary edition features
    </div>
    <a class="accordion-toggle btn btn-mini pull-right btn-inverse" data-toggle="collapse" 
       href="#not-yet-another-daw">
      <span class="caret"></span> learn more
    </a>
  </div>
  <div class="span3 accordion">
    <h3>A social network.</h3>
    <div id="social-network" class="accordion-body collapse">
      Meet other musicians, sound engineers, arrangers, etc.<br />
      Collaborate, comment, share knowledges and audio samples with Claw
    </div>
    <a class="accordion-toggle btn btn-mini pull-right btn-inverse" data-toggle="collapse" 
       href="#social-network">
      <span class="caret"></span> learn more
    </a>
  </div>
</div>
